NAME
    Catalyst::Plugin::Email - Send emails with Catalyst

SYNOPSIS
        use Catalyst 'Email';

        __PACKAGE__->config->{email} = qw/SMTP smtp.oook.de/;

        $c->email(
            header => [
                From    => 'sri@oook.de',
                To      => 'sri@cpan.org',
                Subject => 'Hello!'
            ],
            body => 'Hello sri'
        );

DESCRIPTION
    Send emails with Catalyst and Email::Send and Email::MIME::Creator.

  METHODS
   email
SEE ALSO
    Catalyst.

AUTHOR
    Sebastian Riedel, "sri@cpan.org"

